(4, 'Adam Lewis ''Proprietor''', 8, 1, 4, 2, '', 2, 3, 3, 'Website for importing and exporting of agricultural product.\r\n\r\nHere is the job details\r\n\r\nI have small scale business which i want to turn into large scale business now it located in TX and the company is based on importing and exporting of Agriculture products such as Kola Nut, Gacillia Nut and Cocoa so i need a best of the best layout design for it. Can you handle that for me ?. so i need you to check out this site but i need something more perfect than this if its possible .http://www.agroamerica.com.... the site would only be informational, so i need you to give me an estimate based on the site i gave you to check out, the estimate should include hosting and i want the same page as the site i gave you to check out and i have a private project consultant, he has the text content and the logos for the site.\r\n\r\nNote:\r\n1. I want the same number of pages with the example site i gave you to check excluding videos and blogs.\r\n2. I want only English language\r\n3. I don''t have a domain yet but i want the domain name as (topfarmproduce.market)\r\n4. you will be updating the site for me.\r\n5. i will be proving the images, logos and content for the site.\r\n6. i want the site up and running before ending of next month.\r\n7. My budget is $4000 to $6000\r\n\r\nKindly get back to me with an estimate', 'Scope of Work for Top Farm Produce Website\r\n1. Fresh designing of mock-ups for the website.\r\n2. Development of the website in Wordpress - a content management system.\r\n3. Home-page will have an attractive photo slider.\r\n4. Approx 20 pages designed in user-friendly manner.\r\n5. Enquiry form for visitors at prominent places in the website.\r\n6. Contact us page will show the address with marking in Google Map.\r\n7. Multimedia Gallery Page for photos and videos.\r\n8. A Latest news/update section where latest news/highlights can be displayed.\r\n9. Social Media Linking - Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn.\r\n10. Responsive development to display well on mobile browsers.\r\n11. SEO friendly development.\r\n12. The website will be compliant with the W3C standards.\r\n13. The website will be compliant across all major internet browsers.\r\n', 'Cost of developing a website along with one-year maintenance is US$ 4500 + 5% PayPal fee.\r\n\r\nCost of Domain registration of www.topfarmproduce.market for 1 year is currently around US$ 40 + 5% PayPal fee. It may be a good idea to book domain for 5 or more years upfront.\r\n\r\nHosting Cost for 1 year is US$ 75 + 5% PayPal fee.\r\n\r\nTotal Cost of developing the website with one-year maintenance/regular updates + 1 year domain registration + 1 year hosting is US$ 4615 + 5% PayPal fee.\r\n\r\nNote: After one year, for updating content on regular basis you need to pay US$ 1900 + PayPal fee for our annual support and maintenance package.\r\n\r\nEstimated Time: 3 weeks\r\nNote: If complete website content is provided upfront, we are able to deliver the website in 15 days.', 'May 26, 2015', '2015-07-01', '4500.00', '', 'Adam, Adam Lewis, Agricultural Product', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-07-28 01:58:25', 4, 2),
(5, 'Whitehouselabs - Salesforce', 6, 7, 3, 2, '', 2, 5, 4, 'We are thinking of building a platform for Whitehouse Labs on Salesforce.  We want to track all there Lab Testing and Clients.  It seems like using Salesforce is not that expensive,  it is the development of a platform that works for a business is the tough part.\r\n\r\nIt is called LIMS or Laboratory Information Management Software.  I am trying to get them to automate what they now do in spreadsheets. \r\n\r\n', 'Not Decided', 'Not Given Yet', 'Does your team have any experience with implementing Salesforce for a company that wants to track business flow and client information.', '2015-06-25', '2000.00', '', 'Salesforce', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-06-26 04:34:19', 1, 4),
