(10, 'E-commerce for grocery shop', 6, 4, 4, 1, '', 1, 7, 5, 'Want us to develop e-commerce site for grocery store and data entry for 2500 products.', 'Features\r\n-> Users will be able to login/register into the website. \r\n-> Users will be able to create an account after submitting their name, email id, contact info, etc. on the website.\r\n-> User will be able to browse products under different categories available on the website.\r\n-> Users will be able to search products by using keywords like product name, product category, etc. and they can refine their search by using filters available on the website.\r\n-> Users will be able to view the product with details like images, product description, price etc. on the website.\r\n-> Users will be able to view various special offers available on the website.\r\n-> Users will be able to add the products to the shopping cart.\r\n-> Users will be able to place their orders on the website. \r\n-> Users will be able to use check out feature available on the website. \r\n-> Users will be able to make payment for purchasing items on the website by using integrated payment gateway provided by the client. \r\n-> Users will be able to receive an email for confirmation after an order is placed on the website.\r\n-> Users will be able to choose their mode of shipping using integrated shipping gateway on the website.\r\n-> Users will be able to view the shipping details on the website.\r\n-> Users will be able to provide delivery address for their purchased products on the website.\r\n-> Users will also be able to see the order history, order status, shopping cart, etc. on the profile.\r\n-> Users will be able to track their orders on the website.\r\n-> Users will be able to redeem discounts by using the discount coupons received from the site.\r\n-> Users will be able to view the product prices in multi-currencies. The detailed information about this feature will be provided by the Client. \r\n-> Users will be able to receive newsletter after submitting their name and email id on the website and this section will be managed by admin.\r\n-> Users will be able to share the link of the website on the social networking sites like facebook, twitter etc.\r\n-> Users will be able to view FAQ on the website.\r\n-> Users will be able to browse the site on their mobile devices as we will provide a responsive website design.\r\n\r\nAdministrative Panel\r\n\r\nThe back end of the website will be power packed with an administrative panel to manage the updation of data at the front as well as back end. Following are the key functionalities:\r\n\r\nUsers Management\r\nProduct Management\r\nGeneral Management\r\nOrder Management\r\nPayments Management\r\nNewsletter Module\r\nContent Management\r\nFAQ Management\r\nReports Management', '75,000/-', 'May 22nd,2015', '2015-08-01', '75000.00', '', 'Grocery store, e-commerce', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-06-25 04:41:38', 4, 2),
