(199, 'Partner for e-commerce business ''Joseph Chia''', 6, 7, 4, 4, '', 4, 155, 3, ' Require e- commerce proposal and also the below mentioned inputs:\r\n# List of most recommended eCommerce platforms\r\n# List of other eCommerce platform where we can build the websites\r\n# List of standard features of a eCommerce site\r\n# Approximate cost of a eCommerce site. If it depends on the selected eCommerce platform then the platform wise costing\r\n# Costing of AMC packages for a eCommerce site', 'e-commerce portfolio sent and also replied to all the queries of client\r\n\r\nI would request you to please see the below points for all your queries. \r\n\r\nA) List of most recommended eCommerce platforms\r\n\r\nOpen-source\r\nMagento\r\nWoo Commerce\r\nOpen Cart\r\nHosted\r\nShopify\r\nBigCommerce    \r\nB) List of other eCommerce platforms where we can build the websites\r\nVolusion\r\nZen Cart\r\nPrestaShop\r\nDrupal UberCart\r\nJoomla Virtuemart\r\nosCommerce \r\nLoaded Commerce / CRE Loaded\r\nX-Cart\r\nPinnacle Cart\r\n3DCart\r\nWorking on any cart platform is no issue for us. \r\n\r\nC) and D) List of standard features of an eCommerce site with approximate costs\r\n\r\nMagento Community Edition: please refer attached document "Standard Magento and WooCom Features" for what will be offered in Standard Magento Site set up.\r\nCurrently, we are offering this at a very very basic "grab-any-customer" price of US$1200 and we should expect it to be $1600 in a few months time as Magento is a very very effort consuming and skill intensive work.\r\n\r\nThis includes mock-up designing, magento responsive theme development, store setup with mentioned features, and set up for each page type. Any additional feature and integration is at additional costs.\r\n\r\nWooCommerce: please refer attached document  "Standard Magento and WooCom Features" for what is offered in Standard Woo Commerce Setup - The cost for this is very minimal US$ 850 including mock-up designing, magento responsive theme development, store setup with mentioned features, and set up for each page type. WooCommerce is ideal for small businesses, individual sellers.\r\n\r\nShopify: https://www.shopify.com.sg/pricing - starting at US$ 1100 \r\n\r\nBigCommerce: https://www.bigcommerce.com/pricing/ - starting at US$ 1100\r\n\r\nMoreover, I have also attached a document "Nibiru_Useful and Popular eCommerce Features.pdf". This is a very useful document that we use at Nibiru to work with client in discussing what all features could be desirable for his eCommerce website. They can either be included in Phase 1 of the website or can be included in a phase 2 after the base website has been set up.\r\n\r\nE) Costing of AMC packages for an eCommerce site\r\n\r\n   \r\n\r\n e-Commerce Website Yearly Maintenance Service\r\nScope of Work\r\n1\r\nShopping Cart Version Updates\r\n2\r\nModule Updates when needed to match with the version updates\r\n3\r\nSupport in case something doesn''t work on the website as it should\r\n4\r\nMonthly back-up\r\n5\r\nQuick restoration of the website in case of any attack/malware issue\r\nThe Annual Maintenance Package Price depends on the platform, size and complexity of the eCommerce website. Please find below the standard prices for base websites on the 4 popular platforms.\r\n\r\nWooCommerce, Shopify, BigCommerce: @ US$ 20 per month - $ 240 p.a. paid yearly in advance\r\n\r\nMagento: @ US$ 50 per month - $ 600 p.a. paid yearly in advance\r\n\r\nNote:\r\n\r\n1. Add-on Hour-based Support Packages are available for ongoing support work that client needs or the website demands.\r\n\r\nA 5-hour/month Support Package costs $100 in addition to the basic maintenance package above.\r\n\r\nThis includes but is not limited to designing and updating banners for home-page, banners for category pages, ads, newsletter designing or editing, any design change, any programming change/add-on, new page creation, on-site SEO related work like updating keywords, tags, sitemaps,